  "title": "Architectural Coordinator",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Job\nDescription & Requirements</strong></u></p><ul><li>Project administrations and architectural co-ordination\n     which include preparation of floor layout drawings, shop drawings, door scheduling\n     submission BIM systems and submissions</li><li>Liaise with main contractors and consultants to ensure\n     all the technical requirements are met where applicable</li><li>Must be experienced & proficient in Revit, AutoCAD,\n     BIM and Autodesk and hands on in Autodesk docs , Autodesk build will be\n     given preference</li><li>Minimum of 6 years experience in Architectural\n     Coordination & at least 3 years must be in Singapore</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><p>Candidate must possess at least\nDiploma / Advanced / Graduate Diploma / Bachelor's degree / Professional Degree\nin Architectural , Enginering (Civil) or equivalent</p>",
